Vine,is,a,service,for,mobile,devices,that,allows,users,to,create,and,share,very,short,seconds,or,less,looping,videos,When,a,user,publishes,a,video,to,Vine,it,will,appear,in,their,profile,and,in,the,timelines,of,their,followers,Videos,can,also,be,posted,to,Twitter,and,Facebook,The,Vine,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,data,from,the,service,including,popular,videos,user,data,a,user,s,timeline,videos,matching,a,given,tag,individual,posts,and,notifications